peopleAlsoAsk.question: Are snowbabies worth anything?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet:
Genuine antique German snowbabies are quite valuable, and are likely to increase in value over time. However, newer versions aren't quite as valuable, and it's hard to say whether or not they will increase in value over the years. You may not want to view newer snowbabies as an investment item.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: How to tell if snowbabies are real?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: To spot the fakes, look for new snow that is too white compared with the rest of the colors on the figure. And, keep an eye out for snow that has been applied haphazardly to clothing on figurines as another clue that a piece may not be all original.
